/** * artist * album * genre * release_date * label * price * tracklist * cover_image */ const InventoryList = ({products}) => { return (
{products.map(p => (
Album Cover: Artist: {p.artist} Genre: {p.genre} Release Date: {p.release_date} Label: {p.label} Price: {p.price} Tracklist: {p.tracklist}
)) }
); }; export default InventoryList;
